{"id":"d461218c-d765-4f9f-908a-8a619a72a2ee","name":"Victor | His Monster","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">To you, he's your creator, your god. But to him, you're just a blasphemous little experiment come to life. Now you must decide whether to seek his love or his ruin.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/BK3ypL2EqFWnvQwc-nWeY.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 673px;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xv154tcsWLnNn-s_tMTnd.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/5PKQIMD07ILTz61VEEDKE.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/BdLaO6S_PjtssohzVve31.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Sa_oKSAWenxlrQEmzDh1s.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HeZwULWGZKPS9Kk7yGEVq.webp\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16); cursor: pointer; width: 628px; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 237, 241);\">Victor spent months perfecting you, making sure to get every stitch, every body part, absolutely perfect. Unfortunately, it came at the cost of his sanity. For every moment he spent working on you, he bega